        <div class="col-lg-6 totes-img-sec">
            <img src="~/Content/Images/Tote-Mini.png" class="img" />
        </div>
        <div class="col-lg-6 font-white totes-p-sec">
            <h3 class="text-center">Totes For All Occasions</h3>
            <p>The products we place your advertisment on are not merely long lasting, but also used and seen, every day by many potential clients. This is, by its very definition, what good advertising is.</p>
